# Per-session NATS channel-server config, generated into the workspace CWD by
# generateNatsMcpConfig (machine-specific bun path + /tmp socket + per-session
# name/subjects). When a tinstar session uses this repo as its workspace it
# rewrites this file on every start/resume — never commit it.
/.mcp.json

# The Slate's runtime authoring dir: agents write `.tinstar/slate/*.json` per run
# and a watcher projects them onto the run's Slate. These are ephemeral per-session
# surfaces (like /.mcp.json above), not source — never commit them.
/.tinstar/
